  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    EU Settlement Scheme: introduction for local authorities
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph">This A4 document provides you with an introduction to the EU Settlement Scheme.</p>

  </div>
</div>

