      <section id="details">
        <h2 class="gem-c-heading gem-c-heading--font-size-27 gem-c-heading--mobile-top-margin  ">Details</h2>


        
<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak direction-ltr" data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>Learn about how you as a local authority can support EU citizens and non-EU citizen family members to apply to the EU Settlement Scheme.</p>
</div>
